text:
Music [WATCH] Rappler Live Jam: We Are Imaginary We Are Imaginary is coming to Rappler HQ for a Live Jam! Listen to their full set here Published 6:03 PM, January 03, 2017 Updated 6:03 PM, January 03, 2017 
MANILA, Philippines – We Are Imaginary is kicking off our 2017 Live Jams! 
The band, formerly known as Your Imaginary Friends, released their first LP Death to Romanticism in 2016, and are set to play a few of their upbeat pop songs for us. 
Get to know Ahmad Tanji, Vhall Bugtong, Khalid Tanji, and Eric Jon Po on Rappler Live Jam on Wednesday, January 4. Bookmark this page or head over to fb.com/rapplerent to catch their mini concert! – Rappler.com HOW DOES THIS STORY MAKE YOU FEEL? Happy
